   3.572942040923954*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d85e7371-9a9b-48cb-ab07-\
4ffe56b71096"],

Cell["\<\
And the relationship is confirmed by looking at the correlation between the \
two lists.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.572879280371807*^9, 
  3.572879314337819*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8dfb7c19-42dc-492e-a48e-\
0c9808d2f860"],

